# APEC Chicken RNA-Seq Pipeline — Code Only
**Dataset:** GSE282645 | **Organism:** Gallus gallus | **Samples:** 10 (5 control, 5 infected)

---

## 1. Environment Setup

```bash
conda create -n rnaseq -c bioconda -c conda-forge \
    fastqc trim-galore fastp hisat2 samtools subread -y

conda activate rnaseq

mkdir -p ~/rnaseq_project/{Raw_data,trimmed,QC_report,genome,Results,counts,Scripts}
```

---

## 2. Local Pipeline

```bash
# Download data
fasterq-dump SRR31454337 --split-files -O ~/rnaseq_project/Raw_data/

# Quality control
fastqc ~/rnaseq_project/Raw_data/SRR31454337_1.fastq \
        ~/rnaseq_project/Raw_data/SRR31454337_2.fastq \
        -o ~/rnaseq_project/QC_report/

# Trimming
fastp -i ~/rnaseq_project/Raw_data/SRR31454337_1.fastq \
      -I ~/rnaseq_project/Raw_data/SRR31454337_2.fastq \
      -o ~/rnaseq_project/trimmed/SRR31454337_1_trim.fastq \
      -O ~/rnaseq_project/trimmed/SRR31454337_2_trim.fastq \
      --html ~/rnaseq_project/QC_report/fastp_report.html \
      --json ~/rnaseq_project/QC_report/fastp.json \
      --thread 4 \
      --qualified_quality_phred 20 \
      --length_required 36

# Download reference genome GTF
wget -P ~/rnaseq_project/genome/ \
https://ftp.ensembl.org/pub/release-112/gtf/gallus_gallus/Gallus_gallus.bGalGal1.mat.broiler.GRCg7b.112.gtf.gz

# Build HISAT2 index
hisat2-build ~/rnaseq_project/genome/chicken_genome.fna \
             ~/rnaseq_project/genome/galgal_index

# Alignment
nohup hisat2 -x ~/rnaseq_project/genome/galgal_index \
       -1 ~/rnaseq_project/trimmed/SRR31454337_1_trim.fastq \
       -2 ~/rnaseq_project/trimmed/SRR31454337_2_trim.fastq \
       -S ~/rnaseq_project/Results/SRR31454337.sam \
       --summary-file ~/rnaseq_project/Results/alignment_summary.txt &

# SAM to BAM
samtools view -bS ~/rnaseq_project/Results/SRR31454337.sam | \
samtools sort -o ~/rnaseq_project/Results/SRR31454337.bam
samtools index ~/rnaseq_project/Results/SRR31454337.bam
rm ~/rnaseq_project/Results/SRR31454337.sam

# Read counting
featureCounts -T 4 -p \
              -a ~/rnaseq_project/genome/Gallus_gallus.bGalGal1.mat.broiler.GRCg7b.112.gtf.gz \
              -o ~/rnaseq_project/counts/SRR31454337_counts.txt \
              ~/rnaseq_project/Results/SRR31454337.bam
```

